---
title: Tex-Mex Chicken & Cheesy Roast Veggie Toss with Flatbread Croutons & Smokey Aioli
description: Try a taste of Tex-Mex cuisine with a difference! We're giving golden veggies and baby leaves a flavour boost with tender chicken rubbed with mild spices. Add a dollop of smokey aioli and crispy flatbreads for a feast worthy of a fiesta!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
